      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title XVIII of the Social Security Act to clarify the use of private contracts by Medicare beneficiaries for professional services and to allow individuals to choose to opt out of the Medicare part A benefits.</title>
